name: Happy Rabbit Jumping Around Ass Mountain
description:
..Once upon a time there was a rabbit who had a happy family and a job. Every day in his life was more joyful than the next.

  But one day, some minor problems started in the rabbit's life; His wife found another lover and left the house. After the divorce case, he could not avoid giving alimony.

  After a while, he was fired from his job. Having financial difficulties, the rabbit had to sell its television and some household items.

  He couldn't pay the rent, got kicked out of the house, and nobody wanted to lend him money. One night, he spent his last money getting drunk and got into a car accident. He suffered permanent damage from the accident.

  He became depressed for a short time and survived on medical drugs.

  He moved to this beautiful land away from people and lived happily ever after. Nothing could stop him from being happy.
